Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.04,0:00:18.64,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}The brilliant glow of this sky, does it carry right into your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:28.61,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,1600)\3c&H141414&}The melody you heard in your dream, it plays like the silence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.61,0:00:33.71,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Even if your hands are still far from that dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.71,0:00:38.68,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Come now and remember that kindly voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.68,0:00:51.29,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(50,200)\3c&H141414&}Someone was there singing for you, singing those chords of happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.44,0:01:00.99,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Sound of the sky, echo on high, break through that overwhelming sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:05.83,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Everything that shines in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:11.50,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,400)\3c&H141414&}Is part of the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:20.80,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,200)\3c&H141414&}Even your tears can't leave you here to stay forever
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.80,0:01:33.30,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,4000)\3c&H141414&}In this light pouring down onto you, play tomorrow's song
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.04,0:01:55.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.87,0:02:09.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure feels like fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.50,0:02:14.59,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&00&}One Typhoon Passes - What You Really See
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.87,0:02:19.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so your dad was a tankman?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.01,0:02:24.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. He was part of the platoon that led over a thousand civilians and soldiers out of Wardenburg when it was under siege
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:27.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,with just six Type-2 Millipads.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.61,0:02:31.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A legendary hero during that legendary escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:34.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.24,0:02:35.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.27,0:02:42.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And after he received a life-threatening injury in battle, he met my mother who was an orderly at the hospital he was sent to!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:45.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And you were born out of their love,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.04,0:02:48.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,right, Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:49.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.07,0:02:54.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look like a potato to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:57.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My, what a wonderful potato she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.43,0:03:00.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You raised them very well, Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:06.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We can probably give some to the people in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:09.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And Klaus should be coming soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.57,0:03:12.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we give some to him as a gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:14.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he really coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:18.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You really love Klaus, don't you Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:20.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I like him,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.87,0:03:22.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I just have a lot of respect for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:45.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:49.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! She can even play it like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:51.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:52.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:03.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind is starting to pick up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:07.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather might be taking a bad turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:09.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we stop here for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:10.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:11.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:12.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel, you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:26.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.73,0:04:28.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think Rio's been acting strange lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:30.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What part?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:32.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like her trumpet-playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:34.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it wonderful? It's so smooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.93,0:04:37.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like she's feeling blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:39.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She never did like making small talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:42.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But... Right! Dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.53,0:04:44.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that {\i1}tempura{\i0} delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:47.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! The potatoes were so steamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:48.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:56.78,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are, Rio. Eat it while it's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.78,0:04:57.52,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:04:59.04,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:03.81,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.81,0:05:04.55,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:06.70,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:11.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Bell peppers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:13.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She was practically wolfing them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:15.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio ate them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:16.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.34,0:05:21.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how finely you chop them, she seeks, finds, and removes every last piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.61,0:05:23.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio ate them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:26.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That... might mean something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:42.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:48.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Klaus?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:50.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! It's my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:53.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Desert Wolf, Miracle Klaus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:58.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,On his left breast, he has a tattoo of the insignia of Platoon 481,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:06:00.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,the glorious Wolf Head!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:03.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't he look amazing? You can't have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:09.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you have to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:14.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When the Commander looked down, it was just us worrying, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:18.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:20.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking about Rio,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:23.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,the cool, stylish, and beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:24.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:29.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she just got over her fear of bell peppers and ate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.77,0:06:33.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You really love Rio, don't you Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.67,0:06:36.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always admired her, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.89,0:06:39.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I admire her too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:41.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Noël?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:50.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:03.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for Noël to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:08.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no helping her. I'll give her half of my bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:10.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, take that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:12.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.58,0:07:30.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The fire for the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:32.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot to put it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:34.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I forgot all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:40.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking like you've got everything under control and forgetting one thing is the best part about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:42.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But you've been forgetting too many things lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:44.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:50.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you regretting hanging up on your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:56.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do anything about it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:59.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cover whatever mistakes you make.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:07.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,At least try to be be a cool mentor in front of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:14.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:17.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't sound like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:21.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to come in the middle of the night. Class-1 priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.42,0:08:22.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it addressed to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:27.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Platoon 1121. Master Sergeant Rio Kazumiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:32.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the receipt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:43.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Major, please come inside for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.49,0:08:46.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be going anywhere in this weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:48.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're the Desert Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:52.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.04,0:08:53.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:57.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How about some hot tea and a bath as an apology?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:05.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We appreciate your diligence in completing your mission in this typhoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:11.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry we only have leftovers from last night, but please do eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:18.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have woken me up when Klaus got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:26.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,These are good! Delicious even after it's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:28.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The bell peppers were raised very well too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.62,0:09:30.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:33.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I picked them, and I fried them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.58,0:09:37.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll make a good wife someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:40.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the latest newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:44.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The Major brought it here for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:46.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The peace treaty?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:49.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the conferences still aren't going smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:52.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither side is making any compromises.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:57.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Things would be completely different if Princess Iliya were still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:09:59.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:01.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Iliya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:06.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you can't not know who she is! The Hero of Binnenland!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:09.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The first daughter of Archduke Arkadia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.73,0:10:12.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Goddess of Victory of the Helvetian Army,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.43,0:10:16.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,a tankman as legendary as the Desert Wolf, Major Klaus!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.27,0:10:19.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:21.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:23.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.37,0:10:41.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio! Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:52.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all the ruckus?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:56.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the kids at Yumina's church hasn't been seen since morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:58.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Help us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:10:58.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:00.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister Yumina, who went missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:06.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:11.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an3}Sound of the Skies
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:16.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an1}Sound of the Skies
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.93,0:11:20.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The river's water has risen quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:24.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The fields downstream haven't been harvested yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:27.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dam breaks, they're all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:29.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not familiar with the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:30.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me the way, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:31.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.32,0:11:35.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I am so very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:38.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I only took my eyes off him for a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:41.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Search and rescue is part of our duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:42.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:50.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:50.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:57.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:59.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:08.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:10.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The water is so rough...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.27,0:12:13.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If he fell in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.41,0:12:21.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:23.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:30.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:31.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.72,0:12:35.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You know something, don't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.71,0:12:38.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You came out here because you know where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.07,0:12:42.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! Where is Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:47.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The field.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:48.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Field?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:49.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Eggplants.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:51.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're Sister Yumina's favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:56.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So we all saved our allowances to buy seeds...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.32,0:12:58.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:02.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you plant them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.73,0:13:28.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:31.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In a place like this in the middle of a typhoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:33.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm protecting these eggplants!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:36.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking? Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:38.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're risking our lives for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:41.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You decided to come here yourself! No one asked for your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:43.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:45.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough out of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.92,0:13:56.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up. Kids without parents have to think harder than other kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:14:00.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you cause trouble for people, you know who they'll blame?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:04.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:05.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.75,0:14:08.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll go after your Sister too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:10.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:17.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an orphan too. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:21.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then. Let's head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:23.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:25.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And you still feel like whining?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.25,0:14:26.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.64,0:14:33.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You come to value things that you raise from nothing as much as your own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.05,0:14:39.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Once eggplants are this big, you can eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:44.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll taste amazing if you pickle them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:49.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.65,0:14:52.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Major?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:04.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya has started climbing back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:17.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Major, go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:27.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,N- No. You go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:30.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take up the rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:31.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:02.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're both safe. Thank goodness. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:06.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now there's no way for them to climb back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.14,0:16:10.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation... is grim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:19.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:23.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation has gotten worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.70,0:16:26.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but you're here, Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.49,0:16:29.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll find a way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:34.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:36.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.75,0:16:38.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:44.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up. No need to fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:48.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, Miracle Klaus is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:49.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:52.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The ground is starting to collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.93,0:16:54.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The water's breaking down the soil...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.12,0:16:58.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! This is why I hate kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:17:03.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids who can't listen should just be tied up and locked in a dark room!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:04.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.45,0:17:07.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing will come from panicking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:12.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Those three are always watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:16.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I went too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:19.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,B- But they'll figure something out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:22.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They call Klaus a miracle worker, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:24.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.97,0:17:29.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't the Desert Wolf or Miracle Klaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:34.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They just happened to have the same name and look similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.39,0:17:40.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When they first met, Kureha got excited and decided he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:42.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how Klaus is bad with words.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.07,0:17:46.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He never found a way to tell her, and so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:47.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:53.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we have to find a way to rescue a courier
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:57.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,with only a long service history and an aspiring soldier
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.08,0:17:59.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,without a shred of experience from that ledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:02.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw them a rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:05.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any anchors above them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.28,0:18:09.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're too far away to throw a rope from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.01,0:18:13.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's a way to throw a rope over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:15.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:19.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When I first met you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.73,0:18:25.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that maybe if my father were still alive, he would be like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:32.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I tell people about him like I knew him well,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:35.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but I actually heard it all from other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:37.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:41.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He died before I understood anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:42.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:11.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Left... At attention, signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.02,0:19:14.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Takemicaduchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.57,0:19:20.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:26.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it, Noël?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.48,0:19:29.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Anchor-use linear coil now operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.21,0:19:32.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Targeting system, E-7 to F-5 activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:34.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Initializing aiming system.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:43.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:46.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wire anchor, standby to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.51,0:19:47.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.98,0:19:48.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:19:59.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.59,0:20:06.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you just like your father would if he were alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.01,0:20:09.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.99,0:20:11.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:16.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Standby! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:24.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:27.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:28.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:38.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:40.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Reel in the anchor! Full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:11.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Kureha...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.74,0:21:14.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you now that we made it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.27,0:21:16.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.07,0:21:17.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're exactly what I thought you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.45,0:21:21.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The man I admire most.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:38.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The blue sky after a typhoon passes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:40.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So you played the part the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.99,0:21:42.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Frankly, I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.85,0:21:45.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Never thought you had it in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.57,0:21:51.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When I looked into those eyes, shattering Kureha's dreams frightened me more than death. She believed in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:56.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably how I managed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.74,0:22:00.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I'm just a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.07,0:22:04.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true at all! You were wonderful, Klaus!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.12,0:22:07.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.09,0:22:14.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What someone watching sees and what the person front and center feels are completely different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.30,0:22:19.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The glasses we call admiration are always out of focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.02,0:22:22.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, someone will see you through those glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.28,0:22:25.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll know how it feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.14,0:22:29.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you at least stay until Kureha wakes up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.03,0:22:32.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind telling Kureha something for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.75,0:22:38.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This baby's the best life-threatening injury I've ever had!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.54,0:22:58.10,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - put these feelings together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.46,0:23:01.57,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}And sing of how important they are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:19.33,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I was so happy that I cried
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.51,0:23:25.42,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It hurt so bad that I laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.51,0:23:34.20,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But that all just goes to show that I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:38.80,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,800)}Let's just walk it slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.83,0:23:40.43,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}Everybody singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.52,0:23:44.77,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Just tell me a bit of what you think
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.85,0:23:45.98,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}You're just my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.98,0:23:51.82,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - even though they might waver
Dialogue: 1,0:23:49.41,0:23:51.82,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8\3c&HE5A9EA&}I know, you know, little happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.00,0:23:57.79,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I want us to echo on forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.00,0:23:57.79,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8\3c&HE5A9EA&}Can you hear my precious note?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.16,0:24:03.79,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}All these words that there are can't even describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.05,0:24:09.63,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)}Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.95,0:24:14.58,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)}Can you hear it? Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.63,0:24:25.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(320,180)\c&H020202&\bord0}Next time: Departure - When the First Snow Falls
